{"tid":155191,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[今日笑話] 中國政府出報告談美人權","createTime":"2017-03-13T22:08:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-13T23:30:31.000Z","uid":57376,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"41e4de732c581886f53efb37a81d00dd0eb5ac60","tid":155191,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T22:08:42.000Z","msg":"中國政府在日前出的一份報告中，正式宣告美國傳媒在去年的美國總統大選中偏幫希拉莉。<br />\n<br />\n這份名為《2016年美國的人權紀錄》<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />的冗長報告本月9日發佈，列出美國在2016年違反的人權及公民權利，<span style=\"color: red;\">直接回應美國國務院本月3日發表、針對中國及世界各地的《2016年國別人權報告》。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國的報告在「政治權利遭到踐踏」部份，指責「主流媒體缺乏客觀中立」，「2016年選舉中美國主流媒體大量充滿偏見和特定立場的報道評論，充分暴露了其既不客觀又不中立的本質。」<br />\n<br />\n報告並說：「美國媒體對總統選舉的報道表現出鮮明的黨派政治立場。根據加州大學聖巴巴拉分校進行的調查，全美100家報紙中有57家支持民主黨總統候選人，2家支持共和黨總統候選人。」<br />\n<br />\n美國《華盛頓時報》/新華社"},{"pid":"d2a79c5dfb2f0720bc51b5295622e4de1c1a7bc5","tid":155191,"uid":60665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T22:11:55.000Z","msg":"同孔子和平獎一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69505fa6a58d2c9cb9ac5657b1155a243317669b","tid":155191,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T22:18:47.000Z","msg":"全支那所有報紙支持共產黨 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c69040041ef043337cfe50714dab009b402690c8","tid":155191,"uid":3103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T22:27:27.000Z","msg":"真係笑話嚟"},{"pid":"a30725c7b8a7fdc0c416d4441f0be7bbac3c7070","tid":155191,"uid":37666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T22:39:39.000Z","msg":"冇人權國家談人權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e8ce7ff0f27e2af09c898dc1eb72c177e60beac","tid":155191,"uid":58862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T22:41:34.000Z","msg":"兩個冇人權既國家談人權"},{"pid":"02075e43a58168c47710ac26963749678053ac9c","tid":155191,"uid":52358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T23:30:31.000Z","msg":"太監敎人扑嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}